Notebook[{
Cell["QSP / QSVT Unification \[LongDash] Interactive Notebook", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"c51f1c1a-99e1-5745-891f-aaba3601cdb5"],

Cell["\<\
Executable companion to the QSP/QSVT pipeline reproducing the core \
constructions of Martyn, Rossi, Tan & Chuang, \"Grand Unification of Quantum \
Algorithms\" (PRX Quantum 2, 040203, 2021) and the QSP Hamiltonian-simulation \
construction of Low & Chuang, \"Optimal Hamiltonian Simulation by Quantum \
Signal Processing\" (PRL 118, 010501, 2017). Outputs shown here were \
generated by make_notebook.wls; re-evaluate any cell to reproduce. Convention \
(Wx): W(a)=e^{i arccos(a) X}, S(\[Phi])=e^{i \[Phi] Z}, P(a)=\
\[LeftAngleBracket]0|U|0\[RightAngleBracket].\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2465aacc-3c91-ff48-a34e-96f0bb655187"],

Cell["Setup \[LongDash] load the package", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"35f3c406-26c9-3549-8c6a-c58116d4b166"],

Cell["Loads the reusable package from this notebook's own folder.", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"d4d64f70-fc00-fe41-b4a7-2c4a2404d090"],

Cell["\<\
SetDirectory[NotebookDirectory[]];
Get[FileNameJoin[{NotebookDirectory[], \"src\", \"QSPUnification.wl\"}]];\
\>", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"0e3d995d-0111-8e4f-a7a0-8d99090e3b72"],

Cell["Demo 1 \[LongDash] QSP \[DoubleLongRightArrow] Chebyshev polynomials", \
"Section",ExpressionUUID->"7e8aae1b-a6c0-1b4f-ba1d-70faa3bda9ef"],

Cell["\<\
Symbolic derivation: zero-phase QSP of degree d yields P = T_d and Q = \
U_{d-1}, satisfying the Pell/Chebyshev identity T_d^2+(1-a^2)U_{d-1}^2=1.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"1557e855-0e2a-db45-a732-43faca5e85a6"],

Cell["Dataset[Table[ChebyshevDerivation[d], {d, 1, 6}]]", "Input",ExpressionUUID->"28911e5a-e2a8-d342-b063-03ecd2e4a623"],

